summary: Tony Stark x reader - say you love me  Could you please do a Tony x reader with “If a zombie bit you, I’d be heartbroken, but...
body:
Tony Stark x reader - say you love me

Could you please do a Tony x reader with “If a zombie bit you, I’d be heartbroken, but I’d also shoot you twice in the head.”💞😂 - Anon❤️

Tony insisted on having a horror movie marathon with everyone. You didn’t mind it, just all his choices were crappy.

“Can’t we watch something better?” You whined.

“This is classic!”

“It’s crap!”

“Shut two you two!” Nat snapped.

Both of you snickered but did as she asked. When you weren’t looking Tony shuffled closer until you felt his knee bump into yours. His shoulder brushed again you. You subconsciously leaned into his side enjoying the warmth is provided.

“Hey (N/N)?” He whispered.

Tony lowered his head to whisper in your ear.

“What?”

“What would you do if I got bit by a zombie?”

You stopped for a moment, turning your head to him, getting closer to his face. You knew Tony wanted to kiss you, so you pressed a hand to his chest.

“If a zombie bit you, I’d be heartbroken, but I’d also shoot you in the head twice.”

Tony smirked and got a little bit closer until you could feel the breath on your lips. His gazing flicking the them and back up.

“Heartbroken huh? Wait… why twice?!”

You leaned in, brushing your lips against his as your smirked. Shrugged a little.

“Only because no one would buy me pizza. That and one to kill you, one for fun.”

Jumping up you sprinted out of the room, hearing Tony’s footsteps right behind you. Squealing when he wrapped his arms around your waist.

“Tony!!”

“Say it! You looooove me!”

You wiggled a little, turning in his arms, wrapping your legs around his torso. Pressing a kiss to his nose, and bumping your foreheads.

“I love you Tony.”

“I love you too babe.”

TAGS:

Marvel: @emiwrites3reads @ncisdeaf16 @darth-dorle @stiffinme @startrekkingaroundasgard

All: @sitkafay @havlindzk @drakelover78

by sapphirestark

“Shut it, kid,” the second gunman snarled, his weapon now pointing at Peter. Which would be fine if his friends weren’t directly behind him, only barely protected by a table and some chairs.

He strained his hearing for sirens but couldn’t make them out yet. Instead, he heard Flash whisper “Parker’s gone fucking crazy”. He slowly took steps sideways, away from his teammates, to get them out of the possible shooting radius.

“I’m just saying. Five years minimum. All that for ten grand?”

summary: here’s how mcu stevetony can still win: steve needs to convince both of tony’s sons that he is a good person. this will endear...
question: here’s how mcu stevetony can still win: steve needs to convince both of tony’s sons that he is a good person. this will endear both of them to him. tony will spend time with him because he adores his sons and would do anything for them. steve then needs to find somewhere safe and tony-approved to ditch the kids (i’m thinking a science museum) so that he can get tony alone and have a heartfelt declaration of love. tony, having been wooed by steve’s quality parenting skills, will take steve back.
answer: Steve proposes to Tony underneath a recreation of Leonardo Da Vinci’s original helicopter design and both Peter and Harley won’t let Tony accept until Steve buys them dinosaur plushies from the gift shop.
